cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about active learning for text classification using convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of neural models and word embeddings, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the importance of selecting informative instances, which is a common problem in information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
